sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as Client or Document Processor
    participant API as FastAPI API
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant Worker as Background Worker
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline Stages

    Client->>API: POST /api/upload (PDF, optional bank)
    API->>API: Validate PDF signature and file extension
    API->>API: Persist original PDF to uploads/
    API->>DB: Insert ProcessingJob(status=queued)
    API-->>Client: 202-style response with job_id

    API->>Worker: Submit background task
    Worker->>DB: Update job to processing/extractor
    Worker->>Pipeline: Extractor
    Worker->>DB: Update stage to cleanser
    Worker->>Pipeline: Data cleanser
    Worker->>DB: Update stage to regex_classifier
    Worker->>Pipeline: Regex classifier

    alt Unclassified lines and ANTHROPIC_API_KEY present
        Worker->>DB: Update stage to ai_classifier
        Worker->>Pipeline: AI classifier
    end

    alt Pipeline succeeds
        Worker->>DB: Update job status to completed and link statement_id
        Client->>API: GET /api/jobs/{job_id}/status
        API-->>Client: completed
        Client->>API: GET /api/jobs/{job_id}
        API-->>Client: Statement metadata and classified lines
    else Pipeline fails
        Worker->>DB: Update job status to failed with error_message
        Client->>API: GET /api/jobs/{job_id}/status
        API-->>Client: failed + error details
    end